1981;;Back Roads;;American;;Martin Ritt;;Sally Field, Tommy Lee Jones;;romantic comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Back_Roads_(film);;Amy Post is a $20-a-trick hooker in Mobile, Alabama. One night she entertains Elmore Pratt, an ex-boxer who has just been fired from his job at a car wash. He cannot pay her for services rendered.<br><br>Pratt punches a plainclothes police officer. He and the prostitute drive away together, intending to head for California, bickering along the way.